The energy from

37:42.750 --> 37:44.750
the field generator

37:44.792 --> 37:46.709
down on the planet

37:46.750 --> 37:48.542
simply reflects off of elements

37:46.750 --> 37:48.542
in the converter,

37:48.583 --> 37:52.417
which turns it into

37:48.583 --> 37:52.417
highly focused Krieger waves.

37:52.458 --> 37:54.250
And those same

37:52.458 --> 37:54.250
waves have been

37:54.291 --> 37:56.208
randomly striking

37:54.291 --> 37:56.208
different areas

37:54.291 --> 37:56.208
of our ship

37:56.250 --> 37:57.875
as we orbit

37:56.250 --> 37:57.875
the planet

37:57.917 --> 38:00.917
and our angle to the

37:57.917 --> 38:00.917
generator changes.

38:00.959 --> 38:04.166
Why would Dr. Apgar lie

38:00.959 --> 38:04.166
about his success?

38:04.208 --> 38:09.166
Computer, run

38:04.208 --> 38:09.166
Manua Program One,

38:04.208 --> 38:09.166
time index 14-3-8.

38:11.125 --> 38:14.917
Manua, someday

38:11.125 --> 38:14.917
I'll be able

38:11.125 --> 38:14.917
to reward you

38:14.959 --> 38:16.792
for all your patience.

38:16.834 --> 38:20.417
I'll get you everything

38:16.834 --> 38:20.417
you ever dreamed of.

38:20.458 --> 38:23.000
I have all the reward I need.

38:23.041 --> 38:24.959
PICARD:

38:23.041 --> 38:24.959
Freeze program.

38:25.000 --> 38:32.083
Computer, run Riker Program Two,

38:25.000 --> 38:32.083
time index 16-1-0.

38:35.667 --> 38:37.417
To your success, Doctor.

38:37.458 --> 38:40.250
And the rewards

38:37.458 --> 38:40.250
that come with it.

38:40.291 --> 38:42.375
PICARD:

38:40.291 --> 38:42.375
Freeze.

38:42.417 --> 38:44.375
I never said that.

38:44.417 --> 38:46.500
Nevertheless,

38:44.417 --> 38:46.500
it seems clear

38:44.417 --> 38:46.500
that your husband

38:46.542 --> 38:49.542
was motivated to

38:46.542 --> 38:49.542
earn the rewards

38:46.542 --> 38:49.542
that pleased you,

38:49.583 --> 38:51.166
Mrs. Apgar.

38:51.208 --> 38:52.291
What's wrong with that?

38:52.333 --> 38:53.959
TROI:

38:52.333 --> 38:53.959
Well, he

38:52.333 --> 38:53.959
wouldn't have

38:54.000 --> 38:56.959
earned great profits from

38:54.000 --> 38:56.959
his dealings with Starfleet.

38:57.000 --> 38:59.709
We were only interested

38:57.000 --> 38:59.709
in a new power source.

38:59.750 --> 39:01.959
But if he could turn this

38:59.750 --> 39:01.959
into a weapon,

39:02.000 --> 39:03.458
it would be worth a lot

39:03.500 --> 39:05.625
to the Romulans, the Ferengi,

39:03.500 --> 39:05.625
and a few others.

39:05.667 --> 39:08.667
Now, Dr. Apgar had been ordering

39:05.667 --> 39:08.667
extra dicosilium for months.

39:08.709 --> 39:10.291
That's a pretty good indication

39:10.333 --> 39:11.750
that he was trying to create

39:10.333 --> 39:11.750
larger reflective coils.

39:11.792 --> 39:14.667
And when the away team

39:11.792 --> 39:14.667
arrived early,

39:14.709 --> 39:16.000
he must have been worried

39:16.041 --> 39:18.208
that Starfleet

39:16.041 --> 39:18.208
was becoming suspicious.

39:20.000 --> 39:22.417
He needed more time

39:20.000 --> 39:22.417
to finish his work.

39:22.458 --> 39:25.125
Apgar said that

39:22.458 --> 39:25.125
in each of the three versions.

39:25.166 --> 39:28.417
No doubt he was afraid

39:28.458 --> 39:31.542
that Commander Riker

39:28.458 --> 39:31.542
might learn the truth

39:31.583 --> 39:34.875
and cut off his support

39:31.583 --> 39:34.875
prematurely.

39:38.625 --> 39:40.750
Discovering

39:38.625 --> 39:40.750
Commander Riker

39:38.625 --> 39:40.750
with his wife

39:40.792 --> 39:43.083
didn't help matters.

39:43.125 --> 39:46.709
I submit he

39:43.125 --> 39:46.709
decided to murder

39:43.125 --> 39:46.709
Commander Riker.

39:46.750 --> 39:49.542
Ridiculous.

39:49.583 --> 39:51.208
Is it?

39:51.250 --> 39:54.417
Computer, run Tayna

39:51.250 --> 39:54.417
Program Four,

39:54.458 --> 39:58.750
time index 18-1-4.

40:01.750 --> 40:04.291
I'll contact the authorities.

40:04.333 --> 40:07.917
No... I'll take

40:04.333 --> 40:07.917
care of that.

40:09.959 --> 40:12.083
PICARD:

40:09.959 --> 40:12.083
Freeze.

40:12.125 --> 40:14.917
Tayna, what exactly

40:12.125 --> 40:14.917
is Apgar doing here?

40:14.959 --> 40:18.041
Activating the generator

40:14.959 --> 40:18.041
on the planet.

40:18.083 --> 40:20.041
Now, why would he do that?

40:20.083 --> 40:23.542
Maybe he was going to work

40:20.083 --> 40:23.542
on the converter.

40:23.583 --> 40:24.834
I don't know.

40:24.875 --> 40:26.959
Maybe he was already

40:24.875 --> 40:26.959
thinking ahead

40:27.000 --> 40:30.083
to his next confrontation

40:27.000 --> 40:30.083
with Commander Riker.

40:30.125 --> 40:32.875
Computer, play

40:30.125 --> 40:32.875
Riker Program Four,

40:32.917 --> 40:36.792
time index 24-1.

40:39.500 --> 40:40.750
What are you going

40:39.500 --> 40:40.750
to put in your

40:39.500 --> 40:40.750
report, Riker?

40:40.792 --> 40:42.542
That there's

40:40.792 --> 40:42.542
no justification

40:42.583 --> 40:44.083
for all the

40:42.583 --> 40:44.083
extra dicosilium

40:42.583 --> 40:44.083
I've requested?

40:44.125 --> 40:46.417
That is why they sent

40:44.125 --> 40:46.417
you early, isn't it?

40:46.458 --> 40:47.709
Doctor...

40:47.750 --> 40:49.250
I can explain

40:47.750 --> 40:49.250
why I needed it.

40:49.291 --> 40:51.458
They have no idea

40:49.291 --> 40:51.458
what my problems are.

40:51.500 --> 40:53.000
There are

40:51.500 --> 40:53.000
explanations for...

40:53.041 --> 40:54.500
I don't need explanations.

40:54.542 --> 40:56.333
PICARD:

40:54.542 --> 40:56.333
Freeze.

40:56.375 --> 40:58.959
To Apgar, this must have

40:56.375 --> 40:58.959
seemed as though

40:59.000 --> 41:01.333
Commander Riker

40:59.000 --> 41:01.333
were confirming

40:59.000 --> 41:01.333
his worst fears,

41:01.375 --> 41:03.959
and I believe it was now

41:04.000 --> 41:06.208
that he finally decided

41:04.000 --> 41:06.208
to kill him.

41:06.250 --> 41:08.208
KRAG:

41:06.250 --> 41:08.208
You forget, Picard.

41:08.250 --> 41:12.208
We know that the energy pulse

41:08.250 --> 41:12.208
which blew up the reactor

41:12.250 --> 41:15.000
originated from

41:12.250 --> 41:15.000
Commander Riker's position

41:15.041 --> 41:16.542
not Dr. Apgar's.

41:16.583 --> 41:19.083
Hmm... We are hypothesizing

41:19.125 --> 41:21.417
that Dr. Apgar energized

41:19.125 --> 41:21.417
the converter

41:21.458 --> 41:24.000
at the moment

41:21.458 --> 41:24.000
of Commander

41:21.458 --> 41:24.000
Riker's beam-out,

41:24.041 --> 41:26.542
hoping to make his

41:24.041 --> 41:26.542
death look like a

41:24.041 --> 41:26.542
transporter accident,

41:26.583 --> 41:28.250
but something

41:26.583 --> 41:28.250
went wrong.

41:28.291 --> 41:31.000
The energy pulse hit

41:28.291 --> 41:31.000
the transporter beam

41:31.041 --> 41:32.417
and reflected back

41:32.458 --> 41:35.250
to the reactor,

41:32.458 --> 41:35.250
which caused

41:32.458 --> 41:35.250
the explosion.

41:35.291 --> 41:39.333
An interesting hypothesis,

41:35.291 --> 41:39.333
but impossible to prove.

41:39.375 --> 41:41.542
LA FORGE:

41:39.375 --> 41:41.542
Not really.

41:41.583 --> 41:43.291
We know that field generator

41:41.583 --> 41:43.291
on the planet

41:43.333 --> 41:45.625
has been repeating a discharge

41:43.333 --> 41:45.625
ever since the explosion.

41:45.667 --> 41:46.917
The intervals are like clockwork

41:46.959 --> 41:49.375
<i>except</i> the explosion occurred

41:49.417 --> 41:53.417
.0014 seconds

41:49.417 --> 41:53.417
after the initial discharge.

41:53.458 --> 41:55.208
Now, the only explanation

41:53.458 --> 41:55.208
for that variance

41:55.250 --> 41:57.834
is the time it would take

41:55.250 --> 41:57.834
the energy pulse to bounce back

41:57.875 --> 42:00.250
from the transporter

41:57.875 --> 42:00.250
beam to the reactor.

42:00.291 --> 42:02.458
We've arranged a demonstration

42:00.291 --> 42:02.458
to illustrate.

42:02.500 --> 42:05.000
Mr. La Forge, I think

42:02.500 --> 42:05.000
it's about time, isn't it?

42:05.041 --> 42:08.166
Computer, load program

42:05.041 --> 42:08.166
La Forge One.

