Coordinate auto-engage

42:08.208 --> 42:11.792
time sequence.

42:11.834 --> 42:13.625
The next discharge

42:11.834 --> 42:13.625
from the field generator

42:13.667 --> 42:16.041
is scheduled to

42:13.667 --> 42:16.041
occur in just

42:13.667 --> 42:16.041
a few moments.

