Now, we've aligned

42:16.083 --> 42:17.792
the holodeck program

42:17.834 --> 42:19.375
to re-create the final events

42:19.417 --> 42:21.542
as Commander Riker

42:19.417 --> 42:21.542
described them,

42:21.583 --> 42:24.709
only this time, our facsimile

42:21.583 --> 42:24.709
will automatically process

42:24.750 --> 42:26.709
the energy charge

42:24.750 --> 42:26.709
from the planet

42:26.750 --> 42:29.709
and reflect it just

42:26.750 --> 42:29.709
as the original converter did

42:29.750 --> 42:31.291
before the explosion.

42:31.333 --> 42:35.709
If we're correct,

42:31.333 --> 42:35.709
