42:35.750 --> 42:39.709
COMPUTER:

42:35.750 --> 42:39.709
Auto-engage time sequence

42:35.750 --> 42:39.709
synchronized.

42:39.750 --> 42:41.542
Then we have

42:39.750 --> 42:41.542
nothing further

42:41.583 --> 42:43.458
to say to each other.

